    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 id="build-heading">Internal AI Tools We Build</h2>
      <p style="color:#42474e; font-size:1.0625rem;">Common examples, not the limit of what's possible. All deployed in your environment, on your data, with your access controls. If you have a specific tool in mind that isn't listed, bring it to us.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="builds-grid">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="icon-box"><span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="color:#006875; font-size:24px;">menu_book</span></div>
        <h3>Company Knowledge Base AI</h3>
        <p style="color:#42474e; font-size:0.875rem; line-height:1.7;">Ask any question and get a precise answer with source citations, trained on your SOPs, policies, product docs, and FAQs.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="icon-box"><span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="color:#006875; font-size:24px;">support_agent</span></div>
