        <p style="color:#42474e; font-size:0.875rem; line-height:1.7;">A 24/7 AI colleague that handles HR questions, IT tickets, onboarding queries, and internal requests, instantly and accurately.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="icon-box"><span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="color:#006875; font-size:24px;">monitoring</span></div>
        <h3>Custom Analytics Dashboards</h3>
        <p style="color:#42474e; font-size:0.875rem; line-height:1.7;">Real-time visibility into your business metrics. Ask your dashboard questions in plain English and get charts, summaries, and forecasts.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="icon-box"><span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="color:#006875; font-size:24px;">search</span></div>
        <h3>AI-Powered Document Search</h3>
        <p style="color:#42474e; font-size:0.875rem; line-height:1.7;">Find anything in your company's documents, emails, and files. Not keyword search, but semantic understanding of what you're actually looking for.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="icon-box"><span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="color:#006875; font-size:24px;">auto_awesome</span></div>
        <h3>AI Content &amp; Writing Tools</h3>
        <p style="color:#42474e; font-size:0.875rem; line-height:1.7;">AI writing assistants trained on your brand voice. Draft proposals, reports, emails, and presentations that sound like your company.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="icon-box"><span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="color:#006875; font-size:24px;">school</span></div>
        <h3>Onboarding &amp; Training AI</h3>
