        <p style="color:#42474e; font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.7;">Average time for a new hire to reach full productivity without structured knowledge transfer. Internal AI compresses this timeline significantly by giving new employees instant access to institutional knowledge.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:#fff; border:1px solid rgba(186,26,26,0.15); border-radius:16px; padding:1.75rem;">
        <div style="font-size:2rem; font-weight:800; color:#ba1a1a; line-height:1; margin-bottom:0.75rem;">High risk</div>
