        <p style="color:#42474e; font-size:0.8125rem; line-height:1.6;">We inventory your documents, wikis, and data sources, then identify what to include and how to structure it.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="process-circle">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="color:#00e3fd; font-size:22px;">settings</span>
        </div>
        <span style="color:#006875; font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.05em; margin-bottom:4px;">Step 2</span>
