        <p style="color:#42474e; font-size:0.8125rem; line-height:1.6;">We ingest your data, configure the AI, set access permissions, and build the interface your team will actually use.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="process-circle">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="color:#00e3fd; font-size:22px;">fact_check</span>
        </div>
